<head>DEMOCRACY</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">民主</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>DOCTRINE that RULERS SHOULD be ELECTED by the PEOPLE AND that GOVERNMENT SHOULD BE CONFORMING to the DESIRES AND NEEDS of the PEOPLE.</p>
    </div>
